Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些是綿蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吃掉空氣中的冷氣 長出羊毛一般的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以到了夏天總會變多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是今年太多了點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它們是鄰居嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 應該說比較接近生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過大部分人都看不見它們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它們的毛很適合製作魔法、魔術相關的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔莉卡也經常找我要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有多的話 就做成枕頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該會很好睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說不定能做你想做的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想做的夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剪完後我想拿點走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要剪腳的部分 剪身體就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 能麻煩早點說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}量還真多 我去拿袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世就繼續練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果有不太一樣的蟲 先跟我說聲再碰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本來想一回來就跟他說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但不知道找什麼時機跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說起來我也不知道要跟他說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}時機 時機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他那麼嚴肅 不會幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟他說話有這麼難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟其他的不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 那隻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯說碰之前先告訴他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道碰到會怎樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}火也沒用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}繁殖成功了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該回原野了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是雪蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟綿蟲不一樣 會吃曖氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它吸走了你身體裡的熱氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世沒有碰它 是它自己撞過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來到夏天的繁殖期 肚子很餓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在得保暖一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經暖多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不如說有點熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他去巡邏攔住雪蟲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 我馬上起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不在的時候 我覺得很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但現在這樣和你在一起 卻很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}時機…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在龍之國怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有蛇一樣的巨龍潛在河底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有跳舞的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有在魔法下綻放的花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}林德爾跟我說了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有奈威也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奈威？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們給了我很大的鼓勵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 我看起來好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來你那時醒著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在問林德爾之前 我都以為自己是做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我純粹只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不需要記得這種事 懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為這關係到我很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}絕對不會不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一時衝動真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 你真的不怕我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好像覺得我很害怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為在人類看來 我就是很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也有過家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有母親 父親 和年幼的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}父母也都能看得見怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們的感情也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然總會有怪物靠近讓我很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但只要父親在身邊 就是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一天父親帶著弟弟離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想母親她可能是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以拋下我 離開了人世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我非常喜歡我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但他們都沒有帶我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我原本是…不想再有家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你卻認我是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他口中的未來永遠不會少了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我覺得 自己能和他走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為是家人 就很想了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是你什麼都不肯對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以林德爾跟我說你的過去時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我怕的不是你 而是怕被你拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類會說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這點我無法否認
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我相信智世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為你是我的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有了怎樣的感覺 才算是重視一個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是怎麼察覺的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說過自己很難與人感同身受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以把你對我說的話說回去 就是撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不在時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得非常冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 你會如何表達這種感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該是「寂寞」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來是這樣 我寂寞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他的內心果然還只是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有身體長大了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}買下你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我又多知道了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那在人類的知識上 我是你的老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}挺好的 請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請多指教 魔法老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說起來 我還沒仔細看過你的魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以給我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 和智世的髮色一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我本來想親自給你最後定型的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定要由別人來定型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為它也是幫你走過漫長旅途的手杖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以前輩們會給年輕人的魔杖施加祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}祝福他們能順利走完旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我要做第二根手杖的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就拜託艾利亞斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會耐心等的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你下午有什麼打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我打算學魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他還是不肯跟我談他自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不在的時候 有什麼不尋常的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼 也就小鳥飛來嬉戲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是候鳥還是什麼 有點想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先來學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早 我想要點平時的那種藥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}賽門先生啊 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接骨木果做的果子露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對喉嚨很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩滋華斯一開始也是給我這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我畢竟是負責監視他的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以前也監視過他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我這喉嚨很壞事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那傢伙很貼心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好喝 還是那個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼晚了還有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}屋主可在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}灰之目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽聞出現了新魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}特此前來祝賀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是個活了上千年的老物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三不五時會來找我交流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他並非人類 你要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心 我也沒那麼可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}並未想過要傷害你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:21:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是遠東之地誕生的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有沙石的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說這髮色 還有那雙眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和那島國的人所在的土地 顏色稍有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想必你祖先中 有混雜西方血統的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 我不太了解我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}血緣關係對個體而言 只是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類習慣性地會把問題想太深
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明遵從自己的本心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向束縛我等的一族人的後裔獻上禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}灰之目！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.61,0:22:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Comment: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.06,0:22:35.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}月は見ていた　欠けてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:39.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互いを呼び合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:49.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠回りで　遠い道を歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:59.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}引きよせ合う　赤と黒が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:06.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追いかけ合う　闇と光が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:12.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}二つの対なるもので
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:14.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創られてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:18.28,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この世の総べては
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:25.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あなたがいるから私はいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:31.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}離れてもそばにいる（そばにいる）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:37.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}誰もが自分の　もう一つの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:44.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}片割れという　大切なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:52.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}探し続けてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.06,0:22:35.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}望著月亮 殘缺的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:39.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:49.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}選擇了遠路 並肩啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:59.53,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相吸引的紅與黑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:06.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}相互追趕的光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:12.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}對立的兩種存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:14.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造出了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:18.28,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}世間的芳華絢爛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:25.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只有你在 才有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:31.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們形影不離（形影不離）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:37.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}夢寐以求的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:44.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}屬於我們的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:52.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}我們卻仍在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遵循本能所見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.34,0:24:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是人與非人種之間 無法填補的隔閡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類真是笨蛋呢 而且也很任性

